    Yes, exactly like that. Given your configure line, all of the
    Portland Group's compilers need to work:<br>
    <br>
    $&gt; pgf90 hello.f90<br>
    $&gt; pgcc hello.c<br>
    $&gt; pgCC hello.cpp<br>
    <br>
    What of those commands work for you?<br>
    <br>
    Thanks,<br>
    David<br>
